headline: Did Donald Trump's visit to Georgia change anything?
author: Patricia Murphy
sentences: Our team digs into why Georgia is the biggest test of Trumps influence, how Perdue is taking his complaints about the 2020 election one step further, and why Herschel Walker is taking a different approach.
In a special Tuesday edition of The Atlanta Journal-Constitutions Politically Georgia podcast, Greg Bluestein and Patricia Murphy take a deep dive into what was said in Commerce.
